## FIRST: Read These Files Before Doing Anything

Before making ANY change to this codebase, you MUST read:
1. PROJECT_SPEC.md — what the app does, every screen, every behavior
2. ARCHITECTURE.md — how the system works, data flows, constraints

If you have not read both files, stop and read them first.

