## Quick Reference: SSE Events

```
data: {...}                     — standard OpenAI stream chunk
event: tool_activity            — tool started or finished
event: web_search_results       — web search returned results  
event: content_start            — final response about to begin (may have after_tool_calls: true)
event: error                    — something went wrong
: keepalive                     — heartbeat during long tool execution
data: [DONE]                    — stream is complete
```

